creator: Francis Thompson
description:
LibriVox recording of Poems by Francis Thompson.
Read in English by Christine Lehman; Amelia Chesley; Sonia; Anusha Iyer; Tony Addison; Matthew Datcher; John Burlinson
This is the first volume of poems published by the English poet Francis Thompson. It also includes his most famous poem, The Hound of Heaven. - Summary by Carolin
For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
